lead_paragraph: BRENNER--Suzette. Age 88, on January 31st, formerly of New York City. Beloved wife of the late Frederick; cherished mother of Jayne Gottlieb (Ed) and Linda Betheil (Leslie); adored grandmother (''Gammy'') of Lauren and Melissa; sister of Jules Eisenberg and the late Rita Graham. Service Tuesday 11am at Mt. Hebron Cemetery, Flushing, NY.
